N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 13.16 - Severability

State Regulations

If any provision of this Part is held invalid by a court of
competent jurisdiction, such invalidity shall not affect other provisions which
can be given effect without the invalid provision. Notes
